'''约翰·塞尔登'''（{{lang-en|John Selden}}, {{bd|1584年|12月16日|1654年|11月30日|}}）是一位英国法学家。<ref>{{Citation |last= Pocock |first= John |title= The Ancient Constitution and the Feudal Law |place= Cambridge |publisher= Cambridge University Press |year= 1957}}.</ref>

==生平==
[[File:John-Selden-David-Wilkins-Joannis-Seldeni-jurisconsulti-Opera_omnia_MG_0668.tif|thumb]]绘]]
1584年出生于[[英国|英国]][[西萨塞克斯郡|西萨塞克斯郡]][[沃辛|沃辛]]，毕业于[[牛津大学赫特福德学院|牛津大学赫特福德学院]]。1604年进入[[内殿律师学院|内殿律师学院]]。<ref>{{Citation |title= John Selden and Jewish Law |first= Isaac |last= Herzog |journal= Journal of Comparative Legislation and International Law |series= 3 |volume= 13 |number= 4 |year= 1931 |pages= 236–45}}.</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last= Milton |first=John |year=1644 |title= Areopagitica, A Speech of Mr. John Milton for the Liberty of Unlicenc'd Printing to the Parliament of England |place= London |edition= 1 |page= 11  |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nejQAAAAMAAJ&q=areopagitica&pg=PP13  |access-date= 6 January 2017 |via= Google Books}}</ref><ref name= "naturall">{{cite web |url=http://www.dartmouth.edu/~milton/reading_room/areopagitica/index.shtml |title= Milton's ''Areopagitica'' }}</ref>

